        Constructor initializing the Vehicle object .
        Parameters:
        type - the type of the Vehicle.
        model - the model of the Vehicle.
        year - the build year of the Vehicle.
        pricePerDay - the price per day of the Vehicle.
        kilometers - the kilometers of the Vehicle.
        passengerNumber - the maximum passenger number of the Vehicle.
        motorSize - the size of the motor of the Vehicle.
        fuelType - the fuel type of the Vehicle.
        fuelUsage - the fuel usage of the Vehicle.
        transmission - the transmission of the Vehicle.
        doorNumber - the number of doors of the Vehicle including the trunk.
        airCondition - the Vehicle has or does not have air conditioner.
        auxConnection - the Vehicle has or does not have AUX connection.
        numberOfAirbags - the number of airbags of the Vehicle.
        armRest - the Vehicle has or does not have a center arm rest.
        color - the color of the Vehicle.
        numberPlates - the number plates (registration number) of the Vehicle.
        lastService - the kilometers representing the last service of the Vehicle.

        public java.lang.String getServiceMessage()

        Returns:
        message "Service Check: 20000 kilometers exceeded" if the Vehicle has Exceeded 20000 kilometers from last service, else it returns a message containing the amount of kilometers at which the Vehicle needs to make service.
